$ System.Exception (class)

`System.Exception` is the base class for objects that represent exceptions.

In → development/languages/C-Sharp[C#], instances of `System.Exceptions` can be passed from a → development/languages/C-Sharp/language/keywords/exception-handling/throw[`throw`] statement to a receiver in a
`catch` block.

sa:
  → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/try-catch-finally[PowerShell: `try`, `catch` and `finally` blocks]
